You need to set frame for layer in `viewDidLayoutSubviews`:

```
    override func viewDidLayoutSubviews() {
        super.viewDidLayoutSubviews()
        tableView.backgroundView?.layer.sublayers?.forEach { $0.frame = tableView.bounds }
    }
```


